Additional Photography forthcoming- Call with any Questions!

Step into comfort and luxury at 215 Finlee Ln! This expansive property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, offering a generous 2241 square feet of living space. Relax in the cozy living area, complete with an electric fireplace that adds warmth and charm. The spacious kitchen is a delight for cooking enthusiasts, featuring stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher, refrigerator, electric range oven, and a microwave. Enjoy the convenience of an in-unit washer/dryer. The primary bedroom is a haven of relaxation with a huge walk-in closet and an attached bathroom. The community enhances your lifestyle with a scenic walking trail and pet-friendly policies, including a dog door for your furry friends. As an added bonus, this property comes equipped with a 70" built-in TV, a two-car garage, and solar panels for energy efficiency. With its fantastic location and an individual garage providing two covered spaces, this property is ready to embrace you as its new resident. Don't miss outschedule a viewing today and make this exceptional property your home!

Rental terms:
$59.00 Application Fee Per Adult.
Solar included in rent; Resident responsible for all other utilities.
Rental Insurance Required.
HOA fees/deposits may apply.
Lease term: 15 months.
Monthly admin fee equivalent to 1% of the current rent.
One Time Move In Fee $199.
Pet fees and restrictions apply: Pet Move In Fee $199 per pet; 3 Pets Max.
Pet Rent per pet varies based on Paw Score.Breed restrictions apply. Having an unauthorized pet can result in fines up to $500.
Homes are rented in the condition at the time of viewing.
Federal Occupancy Guidelines: 2 per bedroom + 1 additional occupant; 2 per studio.

Please contact us for move-in policy and available move-in date.

Mynd Property Management
Equal Opportunity Housing
License # 9009162

-Fast Online Application
-Mobile App to Pay Rent and Track Service
-Affordable Renter's Insurance

Mynd Property Management does not advertise on Craigslist or Facebook. We will never ask you to wire money or pay with gift cards. Please report any fraudulent ads to your Leasing Associate.
